OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FVernon Kay to replace Ken  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBruce on Radio 2           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Vernon Kay will replace presenter Ken  
OL,6, Bruce on his weekday mid-morning slot  
OL,7, on Radio 2, the BBC has confirmed.     
OL,9,FBruce announced on air in January that 
OL,10,Fhe would be leaving the station after  
OL,11,F31 years in the role.                  
OL,13,F"Vernon is a lovely bloke and I wish   
OL,14,Fhim all the best," Bruce told BBC News,
OL,15,Fadding that he "wouldn't dare give     
OL,16,Fanyone else tips about broadcasting".  
OL,18,FKay, who is known for presenting ITV's 
OL,19,FAll Star Family Fortunes, said taking  
OL,20,Fover the show was "a dream come true". 
